          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"timeline02\" group=\"News\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" value=\"6\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n          <b>志愿活动与社会实践</b></h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image active\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          2018\n        </p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n          <b><br></b><br><b>积极参加各类志愿活动</b></h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><br>迎新志愿者<br>招生志愿者<br>学院100周年学科庆志愿者<br>……</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/1-1256x840.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          2018\n        </p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n          <b>奋战脱贫攻坚，发扬吕梁精神——“牢树中国自信”实践活动</b>\n        </h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <br><i>相关推送：</i><br><i><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/rHz8IOAhhlAttMtbPhGeHg\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">🔗脱贫攻坚</a></i><br><i><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/26iiXpzNj9Adv0FGDnmrOA\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">🔗吕梁精神</a><br></i><br><br><br></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/1728355633372-811x565.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uqwBlfAIy3",
